12
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:17,519
[SPEAKER_03] Šta ti zapisuješ cijelo vrijeme?

13
00:00:20,719 --> 00:00:21,760
[SPEAKER_02] Nam šalam, Baktir.

14
00:00:22,320 --> 00:00:22,559
