15
00:00:23,600 --> 00:00:24,239
[SPEAKER_03] Ajde, ajde.

16
00:00:25,519 --> 00:00:28,559
[SPEAKER_02] Sad sam skužio da si bila dobar izbor za to.

17
00:00:28,800 --> 00:00:30,800
[SPEAKER_02] Da, ovo je, mislim, trenutak istine.

18
00:00:30,879 --> 00:00:32,399
[SPEAKER_02] Ja sam mislio, to gluma, ali to je.

19
00:00:32,960 --> 00:00:33,679
[SPEAKER_02] Brava, jasno.

20
00:00:33,920 --> 00:00:35,359
[SPEAKER_02] Ne znači da si samo neko političar.

21
