627
00:56:53,519 --> 00:56:54,079
[SPEAKER_03] Samo u sebi.

628
00:56:54,480 --> 00:56:58,320
[SPEAKER_03] To se zove dragi humor ili ti suhi humor, ali nasmijati.

629
00:56:58,400 --> 00:57:00,320
[SPEAKER_03] Ajde ti mi reci, šta ti misliš o mom filmu?

630
00:57:09,039 --> 00:57:09,440
[SPEAKER_01] Da čujemo.

631
00:57:12,960 --> 00:57:14,639
[SPEAKER_02] Mislim da je potreban za ovo društvo.

632
00:57:16,159 --> 00:57:16,480
[SPEAKER_01] Ja isto.

633
00:57:16,800 --> 00:57:17,920
[SPEAKER_02] I da je došao u pravo vrijeme.

634
00:57:19,280 --> 00:57:19,360
