636
00:57:31,519 --> 00:57:35,679
[SPEAKER_03] Ajde da opišem je kao autora, dakle, kao čovjeka u vremenu i prostoru.

637
00:57:35,920 --> 00:57:36,639
[SPEAKER_03] To bi trebalo biti više.

638
00:57:38,400 --> 00:57:41,039
[SPEAKER_03] Što veli, kakav režiser, takav film?

639
00:57:43,760 --> 00:57:44,559
[SPEAKER_03] Kako sam ja?

640
00:57:48,719 --> 00:57:49,119
[SPEAKER_01] Sigurna.

641
00:57:50,639 --> 00:57:51,440
