642
00:57:52,079 --> 00:57:52,960
[SPEAKER_02] Ne, želiš to?

643
00:57:53,360 --> 00:57:54,400
[SPEAKER_03] Aha, da, naravno.

644
00:57:54,800 --> 00:57:55,119
[SPEAKER_02] Želiš.

645
00:57:55,360 --> 00:57:55,440
[SPEAKER_03] Da.

646
00:57:58,960 --> 00:57:59,679
